Sentencas: In this article, a new nature-inspired optimizer based on bald eagles' fish hunting behavior is proposed for accurate parameters estimation of the solid oxide fuel cells stack's model.
Titulo: Optimal parameter estimation of solid oxide fuel cells model using bald eagle search optimizer

Sentencas: The optimal estimated values of the seven control parameters are generated by the bald eagle search (BES) optimizer.
Titulo: Optimal parameter estimation of solid oxide fuel cells model using bald eagle search optimizer

Sentencas: These parameters have optimized the model of the solid oxide fuel cells stack and formulated it as an optimization problem with associated constraints.
Titulo: Optimal parameter estimation of solid oxide fuel cells model using bald eagle search optimizer

Sentencas: The employed BES optimizer is a flexible algorithm with a relatively large population size which effectively improves the optimization process and has the ability to be improved.
Titulo: Optimal parameter estimation of solid oxide fuel cells model using bald eagle search optimizer

Sentencas: The BES optimizer is smooth, rapid, and steady in the convergence process.
Titulo: Optimal parameter estimation of solid oxide fuel cells model using bald eagle search optimizer

Sentencas: The BES optimizer is a very simple algorithm that consists of three main stages which are selecting hunting space, searching in the hunting area, and swooping stage.
Titulo: Optimal parameter estimation of solid oxide fuel cells model using bald eagle search optimizer

Sentencas: The model of the stack is tested at four operating conditions at 3 bar and varied temperatures of 923/973/1023/1073 K.
Titulo: Optimal parameter estimation of solid oxide fuel cells model using bald eagle search optimizer

Sentencas: The BES optimizer leads to more accurate parameters with good convergences.
Titulo: Optimal parameter estimation of solid oxide fuel cells model using bald eagle search optimizer

Sentencas: The insignificant values of reported worst mean square errors of something around 4.7e-6 V-2 points out the full conformity and coincidence between actual and estimated dataset voltage points.
Titulo: Optimal parameter estimation of solid oxide fuel cells model using bald eagle search optimizer

Sentencas: In addition to that, the efficacy of the BES optimizer is assured by comparing the results to parameters estimated from some recent techniques.
Titulo: Optimal parameter estimation of solid oxide fuel cells model using bald eagle search optimizer

Sentencas: The cropped estimated polarization curves, V-I and P-I, are very close to the measured datasets at various operating conditions.
Titulo: Optimal parameter estimation of solid oxide fuel cells model using bald eagle search optimizer

Sentencas: Statistics metrics indicate the robustness and the viability of the BES compared to other recent challenging optimizers.
Titulo: Optimal parameter estimation of solid oxide fuel cells model using bald eagle search optimizer
